Last_Value (DATE_ADD (qH_CORRECT_FROM, -1), TRUE) OVER (PARTITION BY qH_IDENTIFIER ORDER BY qH_CORRECT_FROM DESC, qH_VALID_FROM DESC, qH_TIMESTAMP DESC, qH_VERSION DESC ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND 1 PRECEDING)

Case When Last_Value (DATE_ADD (qH_VALID_FROM, -1), TRUE) OVER (PARTITION BY qH_IDENTIFIER ORDER BY qH_VALID_FROM DESC, qH_TIMESTAMP DESC, qH_VERSION DESC ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND 1 PRECEDING) Is NULL AND Last_Value (DATE_ADD (qH_CORRECT_FROM, -1), TRUE) OVER (PARTITION BY qH_IDENTIFIER ORDER BY qH_CORRECT_FROM DESC, qH_VALID_FROM DESC, qH_TIMESTAMP DESC, qH_VERSION DESC ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND 1 PRECEDING) Is NULL Then -1 Else 0 End
